  <brief_title>Double Blind Randomized Trial of Saline vs Pentaspan for Resuscitation After Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Trial of Synthetic vs Normal Saline for the Flow-based Algorithmic Hemodynamic Resuscitation of Patients Post-cardiac Surgery</official_title>
